title: Bobby Announces His Date To The CMT Awards + Lunchbox Negotiates Deal For Attending The Show’s Live Broadcast From The Ryman
itunes:title: Bobby Announces His Date To The CMT Awards + Lunchbox Negotiates Deal For Attending The Show’s Live Broadcast From The Ryman
description:
Bobby announces who he plans to take as his date to the CMT Awards tomorrow night. Lunchbox’s interview with Kelsea Ballerini gets creepy. Also, Lunchbox negotiates his terms to attend the show’s LIVE broadcast at the Ryman Friday.
